data.description: Location and versatility!  This property offers the best of both residential and commercial possibilities! This 3-bedroom, 1-bath home sits on a spacious .73-acre lot with a fenced-in backyard, providing a perfect blend of comfort and potential. Nestled on a generous lot, the property provides excellent opportunities for commercial use. Whether you envision a home-based business, office space, or any commercial venture, the location and space make it adaptable to various needs.   For savvy investors, this property represents a fantastic opportunity to capitalize on its dual-use potential. The strategic location, coupled with the flexibility to cater to both residential and commercial needs, makes it an attractive investment prospect.  Don't miss out on the endless possibilities that property has to offer. Whether you're looking for a cozy home or a lucrative commercial space, this property is ready to fulfill your vision. Schedule your private showing today!
